    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine dei amen. Breve de scriptis causam memorie quod aliquanti homines
                        de <placeName ref="#places/3200" key="#Bridges/pontoons #Monasteries"
                            >Ficeclo</placeName> in dei nomine iuraverunt a sancta dei evangelia,
                        bona fide sine fraude, (â€¦)torium <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3209"
                            key="#Bridges/pontoons">(opere) <rs key="#Bridges/pontoons">pontis</rs>
                            de Ficeclo</orgName> sive nostra pecunia expendenda a furnacem Iohannis
                        que est in campo<orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3200" key="#Monasteries">
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">abatie</rs></orgName> usque a salina et non
                        haberimus in consilio vel factu quo pons destruatur vel contrarietur. Et si
                        quo tempore pons vi atque aliquo modo destructus fuerit, non interdicemus
                        eum non redificari, immo adiuvabimus ut reedificetur. Et nos in aliquo
                        tempore non erimus in consilio vel factu quod passipedium ad pontem Arni vel
                        super ponte Arni inponatur vel auferatur, vel ibi imponeretur. Et si
                        impositum ibi fuerit, faciemus remanere, bona fide, mercede petendo. Et non
                        dabimus consilium vel adiutorium ullo modo in danietate ipsius pontis vel
                        eius operibus. Scilicet <persName>Torpinus</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Rolandi</persName>, <persName>Guido</persName> et
                            <persName>Rolandinus</persName> germani et quondam <persName
                            key="#Viscount">Ugonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Viscount">vicecomitis</rs>, <persName>Ramone</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Enrigi Gualandi</persName>, <persName>Forestani</persName> et
                            <persName>Martini</persName> germani et quondam
                            <persName>Gerardini</persName>, <persName>Duca</persName> et
                            <persName>Parent</persName> germani et quondam
                            <persName>Cechinerli</persName>, <persName>Getholinus</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Rustichelli</persName>, <persName>Uguicione</persName> et
                            <persName>Guidocto</persName> et <persName>Ugolinus</persName> germani
                        et quondam <persName>Perucci</persName>, <persName>Greppaldus</persName>
                        quondam <persName>Assaliti</persName>, <persName>Enrigus</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Tollecte</persName>, <persName>Guidoloctus</persName> et
                            <persName>Guido</persName> germani et quondam
                            <persName>Ruberti</persName>, <persName>Ubertus</persName> et
                            <persName>Sesmondellus</persName> et <persName>Alioctus</persName>
                        germani et quondam <persName>Pylosichi</persName>,
                            <persName>Amadeus</persName> et <persName>Deodatus</persName> germani et
                        quondam filii <persName>Tolomi</persName>, <persName>Ugicione</persName>
                        cambiatori, <persName>Leonardus</persName> filio
                        <persName>Vetuli</persName>, <persName>Tiniosus Accarini</persName>,
                            <persName>Ugolini</persName> quondam <persName>Baroncelli</persName>,
                            <persName>Paganellus Trepponis</persName>, <persName>Matheus</persName>
                        quondam <persName>Drachi</persName>, <persName>Stavalle</persName> filio
                            <persName>Danitti</persName>, <persName>Rolandinus</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Fresingi</persName>, <persName>Ildebrandino</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Oddi</persName>, <persName>Armati</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Tedaldini</persName>, <persName>Gottifredus</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Brunetti</persName>, <persName>Abenante</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Guittonis</persName>, <persName>Ruberto</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Ugolinelli</persName>, <persName>Deotisalvi</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Guittonis</persName>, <persName>Petrus Cairi</persName>,
                            <persName>Guisalbertus</persName> notarius, *** quondam
                            <persName>Ormanni</persName>, <persName>Ardinigellus</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Imbrigati</persName>, <persName>Usasini</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Ansidri</persName>, <persName>Ugobaldus</persName> filio
                            <persName>Getholini</persName>, <persName>Trinciaullia</persName>
                        quondam <persName>Bastardi</persName>, <persName>Martinellus</persName> de
                        Orbignano, <persName>Capricio</persName> quondam <persName>Russi</persName>,
                            <persName>Deotifeci</persName> quondam filio
                        <persName>Parisi</persName>, <persName>Iohanni</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Albonelli</persName>, <persName>Corso</persName> quondam ***,
                            <persName>Enrigus Denie</persName>, <persName>Pinchino
                            Deotisalvi</persName> quondam <persName>Guerri</persName>,
                            <persName>Ugolinello Georgi</persName>,
                            <persName>Bartholomeus</persName> quondam <persName>Greche</persName>,
                            <persName>Parisi</persName> quondam <persName>Tedaldini</persName>,
                            <persName>Talliafecia</persName> et <persName>Torelli</persName> germani
                        et quondam <persName>Tiniosi</persName>, <persName>Guittoni</persName>
                        quondam <persName>Albonelli</persName>, <persName>Bonaiuto</persName>,
                            <persName>Aiuto</persName>, <persName>Ferro</persName>,
                            <persName>Baroti</persName>, <persName>Canamele</persName>,
                            <persName>Baldono Sesmondi</persName>, <persName>Baldoino</persName>.
                        Persone onis (sic) suprascripti iuraverunt sicut supra dictum est. Dominice
                        incarnationis anno millesimo centesimo octuagesimo primo, sexto kalendas
                        iunii, indictione tertiadecima. Ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary"
                            >Guisalbertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> ibi fui et vidi et hoc totum scripsi.</ab>
